    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概要（Overview）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款回合制战术策略游戏——在看不见的战场上，一步之差就能决定生死。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本作中，敌我双方遵循相同的视野规则；与“看不见的敌人”遭遇，往往会导致致命后果。多数攻击会被墙体阻挡，因此地形运用与站位选择将成为战斗的核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都拥有独特的技能与定位。在战斗中达成特定条件后，可解锁全新的技能，从而选择与以往截然不同的战术与玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也可以通过升级来强化已拥有的技能。技能升级不会单纯增加新选项，而是更专注于让你选择的策略更强、更高效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/7061210983c9c18ea6e5c19bb5d6b08b.poster.avif?t=1771868527\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/7061210983c9c18ea6e5c19bb5d6b08b.webm?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/7061210983c9c18ea6e5c19bb5d6b08b.mp4?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索过程中同样可以使用技能——用它开辟新道路，或发现隐藏奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作不强调快速反应，而强调“选择战术并不断强化它”的策略思考。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔹 主要特色</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于视野的回合制战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌我双方共享相同的有限视野规则。<br>看不见的信息，才是最大的威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/3caee6e2a125e6499916727a69345bb6.poster.avif?t=1771868527\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/3caee6e2a125e6499916727a69345bb6.webm?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/3caee6e2a125e6499916727a69345bb6.mp4?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用地形与墙体的战术对抗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >墙既是盾牌，也是障碍——有时甚至能成为武器。<br>潜伏、阻挡、孤立敌人，掌控战场节奏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/df9b895fd4c2d5ee82ee41cc34ae1e7d.poster.avif?t=1771868527\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/df9b895fd4c2d5ee82ee41cc34ae1e7d.webm?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/df9b895fd4c2d5ee82ee41cc34ae1e7d.mp4?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能解锁系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >达成特定行为与条件后，可解锁全新技能。<br>它会带来全新的战斗思路与策略路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/f0f6f7fa3f1639a38391b54aaade243f.poster.avif?t=1771868527\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/f0f6f7fa3f1639a38391b54aaade243f.webm?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/f0f6f7fa3f1639a38391b54aaade243f.mp4?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能升级系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化已拥有的技能，提升其性能。<br>让你选择的战术更具压制力、更高效地执行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/e4a3a741c873c2999d330ddbcbac8069.poster.avif?t=1771868527\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/e4a3a741c873c2999d330ddbcbac8069.webm?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4306780/extras/e4a3a741c873c2999d330ddbcbac8069.mp4?t=1771868527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重视抉择的推进结构</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分岔路口的选择无法回头。<br>每一次决定都会影响后续战斗与整体策略。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >推荐给这样的玩家</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢回合制战术策略游戏的玩家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >偏好利用地形与视野进行战术博弈的玩家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢“解锁新技能改变打法”或“强化既定路线”的构筑玩法玩家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比起单纯数值对抗，更重视判断与选择后果的玩家</p></li></ul>",
